toString

public java.lang.String toString()
Returns a String object representing this TypeScope's value.

If this object represents the change request super type, a string equal to "CHANGE_REQUEST" is returned.

If this object represents the bug or problem report super type, a string equal to "BUG_REPORT" is returned.

If this object represents the work package super type, a string equal to "WORK_PACKAGE" is returned.

If this object represents the other super type, a string equal to "OTHER" is returned.
